rgy density in BL DDM does not exceed\nthe value Espec<(10(8) - 10(9)) J/m(3) decreasing with the growing BL radius.\nResulting indefinitely long BL lifetime is also discussed. BL has no outer\nshell and no any inner rigid or elastic microstructure elements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2010 05:20:52 GMT"},{"version":"v10","created":"Sun, 3 Oct 2010 13:27:07 GMT"},{"version":"v11","created":"Sun, 10 Oct 2010 19:35:42 GMT"},{"version":"v12","created":"Sun, 31 Oct 2010 15:24:28 GMT"},{"version":"v13","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2010 06:59:34 GMT"},{"version":"v14","created":"Sun, 5 Dec 2010 10:59:24 GMT"},{"version":"v15","created":"Sun, 2 Jan 2011 08:01:04 GMT"},{"version":"v16","created":"Sat, 5 Feb 2011 07:20:09 GMT"},{"version":"v17","created":"Thu, 31 Mar 2011 06:25:54 GMT"},{"version":"v18","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2011 08:49:40 GMT"},{"version":"v19","created":"Sun, 5 Jun 2011 07:32:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jul 2010 13:06:15 GMT"},{"version":"v20","created":"Tue, 5 Jul 2011 11:04:51 GMT"},{"version":"v21","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2011 08:21:25 GMT"},{"version":"v22","created":"Fri, 19 Aug 2011 14:00:58 GMT"},{"version":"v23","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2011 09:54:59 GMT"},{"version":"v24","created":"Sun, 25 Sep 2011 12:34:43 GMT"},{"version":"v25","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2011 13:25:24 GMT"},{"version":"v26","created":"Sat, 12 Nov 2011 14:20:08 GMT"},{"version":"v27","created":"Sun, 18 Dec 2011 07:14:00 GMT"},{"version":"v28","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2012 14:55:13 GMT"},{"version":"v29","created":"Wed, 25 Jan 2012 12:40:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 30 Jul 2010 05:33:29 GMT"},{"version":"v30","created":"Sat, 18 Feb 2012 07:49:05 GMT"},{"version":"v31","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2012 23:38:59 GMT"},{"version":"v32","created":"Wed, 25 Apr 2012 08:02:45 GMT"},{"version":"v33","created":"Wed, 2 May 2012 14:51:58 GMT"},{"version":"v34","created":"Mon, 28 May 2012 14:19:30 GMT"},{"version":"v35","created":"Sun, 3 Jun 2012 14:32:18 GMT"},