d abundance ratios in LGRBs hosts suggest that these hosts are\nirregular galaxies both at high and low redshift thus showing that the host\ngalaxies belong to in an evolutionary sequence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Jul 2010 12:26:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Nov 2010 10:09:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-03"}
